	UESP Scripts Collection
	======================
	by Dave Humphrey (dave@uesp.net)
	Created on 6 Jan 2014
	Released under the GPL v2
	
This is a collection of various small scripts used in the setup and administration
of the UESP.net web site.

NOTE: Use these scripts at your own discretion! They are specifically designed for 
use within the custom environment of the UESP servers and may not work correctly
in other environments.


Script Descriptions
-------------------
Basic description of scripts are below. For more information see the header block
in each script file.

	uespdeploy -- Used for deploying various software on the UESP servers.
	uespdeploylog -- Displays the deployment log.
